window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>My entire life has been one steady plan after another.</b></p> <p>Go to college. Get married. Have a successful career.</p> <p>More than a decade goes by, and my entire world is rocked in more ways than one. Everything I thought I knew is ripped from under me in one fell swoop.</p> <p>Then I meet him: the enticing man behind the camera with the boyish grin and charismatic energy who makes me question everything. He was only supposed to be a means to an end. But what I got was so much more.</p>"; 
